videoSnippet.title: Rossolimo's "American Beauty" Reversed - Magnificent Game
videoSnippet.description:
#agadmator Nicolas Rossolimo: "What am I supposed to do, trade in my romantic style and become a hunter of points at any price? No, I will not do so. I will fight for the art of chess. I shall not turn into a monster".

Nicolas Rossolimo vs Paul Reissmann
"La Regina Della Notte" (game of the day Aug-16-2012)
Puerto Rico (1967) 
Italian Game: Classical Variation. Greco Gambit Traditional Line (C54)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. c3 Nf6 5. d4 ed4 6. cd4 Bb4 7. Bd2 Bd2 8. Nbd2 d5 9. ed5 Nd5 10. Qb3 Nce7 11. O-O c6 12. Rfe1 O-O 13. a4 b6 14. Ne5 Bb7 15. a5 Rc8 16. Ne4 Qc7 17. a6 Ba8 18. Qh3 Nf4 19. Qg4 Ned5 20. Ra3 Ne6 21. Bd5 cd5 22. Nf6 Kh8 23. Qg6 Qc2 24. Rh3
